content: This is a great media App. Picks up all my TV shows when other players don't. This is like MX player on steroids, as it doesn't require any extra codecs. +1 for Clean material design and chromecast support. Good job.

I don't have enough words to express how much i adore this video player. I have used other paid apps that made me a bit stressed and annoyed. This video player have super cool and advanced features like floating window, play video as audio & casting support. My most favorite part is it's super clean UI And dark them support. For this price , this video player is best. Well deserved 5 Stars. Thank you!

EXCELLENT Job! I had around 50GBs of videos(TV series, blu-ray movies), and this video player had no trouble finding them in less than 10 seconds. Chromecasting working smoothly. Player Screen features are very handy. Thanks Guys, Good job.
